text: David Breda (born 4 January 1996) is a Czech football player who currently plays for FK Varnsdorf on loan from FK Jablonec. He joined Varnsdorf on loan in August 2017. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Czech footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:FK Jablonec players Category:FK Varnsdorf players Category:FK Dukla Prague players Category:Czech First League players Category:Czech National Football League players
